==Asturian==
===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|ast|fro|jaiole}} or {{m|fro|gaiole}} (modern {{m|fr|geôle}}), from {{der|ast|VL.|*caveola}}, from {{der|ast|la|cavea}}. Compare {{cog|es|jaula}}.
===Noun===
{{ast-noun|f|xaules}}
